data.value: Tahrir Square Hostel in Cairo features air-conditioned rooms, some with balconies, and offers free WiFi, a shared lounge, terrace, and shared kitchen. Located near Tahrir Square and the Egyptian Museum, it provides airport transportation, and continental breakfast. Nearby attractions include Cairo Tower and Al-Azhar Mosque, with Cairo International Airport 11 miles away.
